('Espada Gerlach', 'Legal', 'English-speaking law firm founded in 1980 by Alejandro Espada Gerlach, specializing in international law for foreign residents and businesses in Spain. Multilingual team speaks English, German, French, Spanish, and Catalan. Services include international private law, commercial law, civil matters, inheritance law, labour law, Spanish accounting, Spanish procedural law, Spanish tax law, and corporate/company affairs. Member of Eurojuris España and Eurojuris International lawyer networks, enabling collaboration with offices across Europe. Primary clients include small and medium foreign and Spanish businesses, as well as national and foreign individuals with investments in Spain. Also has an office in Fortià (Girona) serving the Costa Brava region.', 'C/ Provenza 253, entresuelo 2a', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 933 012 741', 'a.espada@espadagerlach.com', 'https://www.espadagerlach.com/en/', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW());
